headline: Synergies Work Reveals Finalists for 3rd Annual EDDIE Awards Celebrating Entrepreneurs with Disabilities
summary: Synergies Work, an Atlanta nonprofit supporting entrepreneurs with disabilities, today announced the 15 finalists across five categories for its 3rd annual EDDIE Awards taking place Thursday, September 25, from 5 to 9 p.m. at Cobb Energy Performing Arts Centre in Atlanta. To learn about the finalists and their respective categories, go here.
